\newlabel{fig:critical}{{5.2}{34}{Critical stops under single-node removal. Bars show the efficiency loss (\%) after removing the same stop from the transfer-based reachability network. Bahnhof, Konzilstr./Theater, and Sternenplatz remain the most critical in both years. Stops that appear only in one year's top~10 are discussed in the text}{figure.5.2}{}}
